What do you think of passing a SnapshotInfo instance to the finalizeSnapshot() but update the end time of this one right before it's written to the repository?
executor.execute(ActionRunnable.supply(allMetaListener, () -> {
                final SnapshotInfo finalSnapshotInfo = SnapshotInfoBuilder.builder(snapshotInfo)
                                .withEndTime(threadPool.absoluteTimeInMillis())
                                .build();
                snapshotFormat.write(snapshotInfo, blobContainer(), snapshotId.getUUID(), false);
                return snapshotInfo;
            }));
